@baseUrl = http://localhost:5006

### Login as Teacher - get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane2@kinderhub.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### Profile - no token (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile

### Profile - with token (expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Admin only - with Teacher token (expect 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/admin-only
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Teacher only - with Teacher token (expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/teacher-only
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE